<p>And the raccoons <em>speak</em>. Instead of the radio signals manifesting in the air, they manifest in the larynges of the raccoons. So if you want to use this for surveillance, you have to go in there and sit among the raccoons with a microphone.</p>
<p>And it keeps affecting new raccoons as they move into the territory.</p>

							</div>

								
					
